  "detailed_description": "<strong>BEARS, VODKA, BALALAIKA!</strong> - is a realistic shooting game in a historic period of World War II of great Soviet Union. You play as generic russian solider trying to defend your Great Motherland with the widely famous AK-47.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129220/extras/de052ecc2baa83142f86f3313a9c3c34.poster.avif?t=1618512781\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129220/extras/de052ecc2baa83142f86f3313a9c3c34.webm?t=1618512781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129220/extras/de052ecc2baa83142f86f3313a9c3c34.mp4?t=1618512781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your main goal is to kill as many enemies as possible and defend the Motherland from nazi occupation.<br><br>Press \"V\" to drink vodka and heal.<br>Press \"b\" to play balalaika.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Truly russian spirit and atmosphere<br></li><li> Shoot legendary russian weapon - AK-47<br></li><li> Drink honest russian Vodka<br></li><li> Play on balalaika</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Trading Cards are now available!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129220/extras/1b8a1a06552ff3d7b56f28079581b391.avif?t=1618512781\" width=600 height=250 /></span>",
